                <p style="margin:0; padding:0; font-size:12px;">Memo
                  NO-RERA/PRO-REG-914/2019/<span>...................</span><br><strong
                    style="text-decoration: underline;"> RERA/PRO-REG/Master File/Misc/115/2021</strong></p>
                <p style="margin:0; padding:10px 0 0; font-size:12px;">Copy to: Chairman RERA/ Members RERA/ A & A
                  Engico Pvt. Ltd</p>
                <p style="margin:0; padding:10px 0 0; font-size:12px;">Copy to: Branch Manager HDFC Bank, Raja Bazar,
                  Patna</p>
              </td>
